 Vulnerability

Thanks for sharing!

Quick fix is to edit file forum/modules/blog/lib/entry_reply_entry.php

and change the following code (line 52 for me)
'where'	=>	"entry_id = {$this->ipsclass->input['eid']}"							
to
						   'where'	=>	"entry_id = '".intval($this->ipsclass->input['eid'])."'"
